history.content: History 124B does count as an upper-division H/SS requirement.  And you are correct, the deadline to change tech courses to pass/no pass for seniors who do not need the course(s) to graduate is Friday, February 20 before midnight.  The last day to change a Humanities course to pass/no pass is Friday, April 3 before 5 pm.  As a reminder, after the 5th week, you will need to come into ESS (230 Bechtel) to pick up a Change of Class Schedule form in order to change your grading option.  You will not be able to make grade changes on Tele-Bears after the 5th week.
